# TRANSLATOR: Displayed when the running kernel version is newer than the
# catalog target version. {r} = running kernel version, {b} = catalog baseline
# version. The em-dash (—) is U+2014. Word order preserved in French.
# WIDTH: longest line fits within normal display constraints.
